<div class="description">
    <h3>Description</h3>

    <div class="body">
        <p>The factory method has been changed which generates a strict standards message if extended like this:
Strict Standards: Declaration of Giata_Uri::factory() should be compatible with that of Zend_Uri::factory()</p>

<p>Old:</p>

<pre class="highlight"><code>
factory($uri = 'http')
</code></pre>

<p>New:</p>

<pre class="highlight"><code>
factory($uri = 'http', $className = null)
</code></pre>

<p>The second argument could be implemented by func_get_args, too.</p>

